point_tooltip: Revythoussa LNG Terminal is located on Revythoussa island. Agia Triada is the Entry Point in DESFAâ€™s NGTS (Natural Gas Transmission System) and is located on the continent. It communicates with the LNG Terminal with two underwater pipelines.

In the integrated management of the whole gas system, SNAM carries out some activities on the basis of an agreement with ITG (capacity allocation and management, balancing). In this context, data for Cavarzere IP are published by SNAM on behalf of ITG.
Until 04/04/2017 Enagas reported the data at Mugardos on behalf of Reganosa, which is the actual operator at this point
The SRG "Sardina Methanization" project allows to match Sardinia Demand with gas supply from different location. This request is general and isn't related to a specific LNG project.
Several TSOs cooperate, capacity is only offered by NEL GT
